<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>10169</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>23672</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>食人魔在房子里走来走去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>23672</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>36246</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他闻着每一个地方。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>36246</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>39945</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>突然，他停了下来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>39945</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>47085</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“Fee！Fi！Fo！Fum！”食人魔大喊，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>47085</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>52856</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我闻到了一个英国男人的味道！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>52856</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>57237</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>不管他活着还是死了，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>57237</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>63768</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我都要把他放在面包上吃掉！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>63768</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>67908</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>躲在烤箱里的杰克害怕得发抖。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>67908</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>71315</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“太可怕了！”他心想，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>71315</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>74151</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“食人魔会找到我，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>74151</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>79863</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后把我放在面包上吃掉！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>79863</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>83886</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>杰克咬着手，不敢哭出声音。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>83886</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>91785</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我再也见不到妈妈了。”他心想，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>91785</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>97629</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“为什么我要拿那些豆子呢……”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>97629</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>103073</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“Fee！Fi！Fo！Fum！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>103074</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>111195</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>愤怒的食人魔又大喊起来，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>111195</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>115746</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不，这不是英国男人的味道！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>115746</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>121488</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这是英国小男孩儿的味道！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>121488</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>127283</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“好了，好了，亲爱的！”他的妻子说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>127283</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>129923</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我什么都没有闻到。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>129923</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>136530</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她笑了笑：“你一定是在做梦。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>136530</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>141359</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我不是在做梦！”食人魔说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>141359</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>146010</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我闻到了小男孩儿的味道！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>146010</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>151339</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>妻子拍了拍他的胳膊：“早饭马上就好了！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>151339</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>154735</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>你要不要先去洗一洗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>154735</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>167631</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>食人魔又开始闻来闻去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>167631</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>173395</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我会做你喜欢的煎饼哦！”妻子急忙说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>173395</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>176090</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>食人魔突然转过头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>176090</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>180164</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“会放蓝莓吗？”他问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>180164</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>186850</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>妻子点了点头：“当然，当然会放，亲爱的！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>186850</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>190055</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>食人魔的肩膀放松了下来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>190055</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>193361</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>表情也放松了下来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>193361</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>202363</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“好，那我先去洗一洗。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>